 class=\"wp-image-624196\"/></figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large is-resized\"><a href=\"https://crocoblock.com/?ref=3457\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><img src=\"https://oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Crocoblock-Black-Friday-2021-Banner-1-1024x536.png\" alt=\"Crocoblock Black Friday Cyber Monday promo banner\" class=\"wp-image-624216\" width=\"768\" height=\"402\" srcset=\"//oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Crocoblock-Black-Friday-2021-Banner-1-1024x536.png 1024w, //oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Crocoblock-Black-Friday-2021-Banner-1-300x157.png 300w, //oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Crocoblock-Black-Friday-2021-Banner-1-768x402.png 768w, //oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Crocoblock-Black-Friday-2021-Banner-1.png 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" /></a></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Sale Start Date</strong>: November 24th 2021.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Sale End Date:</strong> December 1st 2021.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Promo Code:</strong> BFCrocoblock2021 (<a href=\"https://crocoblock.com/?ref=3457\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">promo code must be applied manually on the Crocoblock checkout page</a>).</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Additional WordPress Plugins / Services to Use with OceanWP</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The following partners currently do not offer any Black Friday / Cyber Monday deals, but that doesn&#8217;t make their offers any less interesting. On the contrary.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>1 HubSpot</h3>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><a href=\"https://www.hubspot.com/products/wordpress\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><img width=\"672\" height=\"261\" src=\"https://oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/hubspotlogo-web-color.png\" alt=\"HubSpot logo\" class=\"wp-image-621233\" srcset=\"//oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/hubspotlogo-web-color.png 672w, //oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/hubspotlogo-web-color-300x117.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 672px) 100vw, 672px\" /></a></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://www.hubspot.com/products/wordpress\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">HubSpot is a leading CRM platform</a></strong> that brings a ton of value with its all-in-one WordPress plugin. Over 200k+ users trust HubSpot’s WordPress plugin for adding live chat, forms, CRM, email marketing, and reporting to their WordPress sites.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>2 WPML</h3>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><a href=\"https://wpml.org/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><img width=\"600\" height=\"283\" src=\"https://oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/wpml-logo-tag-line.png\" alt=\"WPML logo\" class=\"wp-image-619676\" srcset=\"//oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/wpml-logo-tag-line.png 600w, //oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/wpml-logo-tag-line-300x142.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://wpml.org/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">WPML is the world’s most popular multilingual plugin</a></strong>, helping more than 700k websites translate their content. It is integrated with the most popular translation services, themes and plugins, including WooCommerce.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>3 Toolset</h3>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><a href=\"https://toolset.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><img width=\"600\" height=\"200\" src=\"https://oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/Toolset-logo-png.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-613165\" srcset=\"//oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/Toolset-logo-png.png 600w, //oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/Toolset-logo-png-300x100.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://toolset.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Toolset</a> makes it easier and quicker for you to build a professional website without complex coding. Whether you are a WordPress beginner or expert you can quickly add advanced features including custom post types, custom search, Maps and front-end forms.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Black Friday &amp; Cyber Monday Deals Summary</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The WordPress community knows it all too well &#8211; <strong>Black Friday </strong>/ Cyber Monday are one of a kind deals you just don&#8217;t want to miss.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>In case of any changes and updates from our partners, we&#8217;ll update the content accordingly.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The OceanWP Team wishes you Happy Holidays (and Happy Shopping).</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0!important;padding: 26px 0 0!important;\"><a href=\"https://oceanwp.org/blog/black-friday-cyber-monday-special-deals-2021/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: inline-block; padding: 10px 30px; color: #ffffff; background-color: #13aff0; border-radius: 30px; font-size: 13px; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.4; text-transform: uppercase; text-align: center; text-decoration: none; letter-spacing: 1px;\">Read More</a></p></p>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:75:\"https://oceanwp.org/blog/black-friday-cyber-monday-special-deals-2021/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"2\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}}}s:27:\"http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom\";a:1:{s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:3:{s:4:\"href\";s:25:\"https://oceanwp.org/feed/\";s:3:\"rel\";s:4:\"self\";s:4:\"type\";s:19:\"application/rss+xml\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explic